### Explain why you need the phone number
Use the optional `label__description` with the [input component](/components/input) for hint text to reassure users why you need a phone number and what it will be used for.

### Make it clear what type of phone number you need
Use the `label__description` for hint text to let users know what type of phone number you need, for example, a UK, international or mobile phone number.

### Allow all phone number formats
The phone number field must accommodate all phone number formats. The length of the field must allow for any spaces or common characters, for example, brackets, dashes or country codes.

### Validate phone numbers

To help users enter a valid phone number, you should:

